{"tid":1299622,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】哩騷攝影師於西藏失蹤","createTime":"2019-07-09T06:01:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T16:00:37.000Z","uid":272435,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"32c73b717df545e4566934235744218d0a404ea9","tid":1299622,"uid":272435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:01:47.000Z","msg":"轉至哩騷轉頁：<br />\n<br />\n（請廣傳）本台攝影師手足Andy，全名簡漢鋒 Hon Fung Kan，喺6月7號出發到西藏，並向朋友報稱計劃六月底返港，但Andy嘅家人由6月16號開始一直同佢失去聯絡，最後知道嘅消息係Andy到達拉薩後，曾入住「拉薩神湖酒店」，目前未有佢返港紀錄，初步估計佢仍然身處當地。<br />\n <br />\n如果有朋友近日到過相關地點，而又見過Andy，或者有認識Andy嘅朋友知道佢嘅狀況，請盡快同豪仔 Aaron Lai聯絡（電話：6323 1506）。感謝。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wRimwPf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwRimwPf.jpg&h=ed32d46a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n目前薯伯伯已在當地了解情況，已知Andy已經退咗房，而家薯伯問緊佢嘅回鄉卡號碼，稍後會再問問拉薩公安嗰邊。<br />\n<br />\n希望各位幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49ada320e1241c7b691c203e59415d74f815250e","tid":1299622,"uid":12864,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:06:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9328677c086653d023b2d016309a2ab7d75b7f2","tid":1299622,"uid":272435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:07:58.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ac133c4d5f14d9c7cd7aa1c11b713bad087cec7","tid":1299622,"uid":272435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:27:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6b077c542f660e784b522ca3fa6edebb63ec3a52","tid":1299622,"uid":235174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:29:55.000Z","msg":"公安請飲咖啡"},{"pid":"54ad0a456620a407625bb578d333a3